{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/extras/f58dfd78-1bd7-41a4-92f9-6b933cf01124.png?t=1735746961\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blue is a 2D puzzle game where you play \u201cBlue\u201d, a little blue cube who wants to change his world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You accompany him on his journey, guiding him through a series of progressively more difficult levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Along the way, you're likely to meet other characters... who knows what links they may have with our little blue cube.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bleu's progress in this world will perhaps enable it to evolve into something better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game takes the form of a series of puzzles, the aim of which is to \u201cslide Bleu\u201d to an objective. However, some of the levels depart completely from the original gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The difficulty increases progressively, but finishing the game is a real challenge. Hundreds of levels, boss levels and a wide variety of puzzles await you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you rise to the challenge?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735746961","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/page.bg.jpg?t=1735746961","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/ef4858f1457b8c9323c2447022f9b025ba65f606/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735746961","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/ef4858f1457b8c9323c2447022f9b025ba65f606/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735746961","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/extras/f58dfd78-1bd7-41a4-92f9-6b933cf01124.png?t=1735746961\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blue is a 2D puzzle game where you play \u201cBlue\u201d, a little blue cube who wants to change his world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You accompany him on his journey, guiding him through a series of progressively more difficult levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Along the way, you're likely to meet other characters... who knows what links they may have with our little blue cube.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bleu's progress in this world will perhaps enable it to evolve into something better.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game takes the form of a series of puzzles, the aim of which is to \u201cslide Bleu\u201d to an objective. However, some of the levels depart completely from the original gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The difficulty increases progressively, but finishing the game is a real challenge. Hundreds of levels, boss levels and a wide variety of puzzles await you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you rise to the challenge?</p>","developers":["Reb"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3368230/header.jpg?t=1735746961","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257075992,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstati